Installation
============

settings_env.py configuration sample
------------------------------------

DATABASES = {
    'default': {
        'ENGINE': 'django.db.backends.mysql',
        'NAME': 'zenon',
        'USER': 'zenon',
        'PASSWORD': 'notsecret',
        'HOST': '',
    },
    'restriction': {
        'ENGINE': 'django.db.backends.mysql',
        'NAME': 'restriction',
        'USER': 'zenon',
        'PASSWORD': 'notsecret',
        'HOST': '',
    }
}

DATABASE_ROUTERS = ['core.subscription.restriction.router.RestrictionRouter', ]


Use
===

Import restrictions
-------------------

python manage.py restriction import_restrictions
